<h2>Life at Technion</h2>

<p>This semester, I join a research exchange program at Technion, advised
by Professor Daniel Freedman. Other than the advanced courses I am taking, 
academic activities I am engaged in and research projects I am working on,
I also enjoy the life here.</p>

<p>We have travelled to Jerusalem, the Dead Sea, Bahaii Gardens, Beach at Haifa and Tel-aviv. Below is a photo of our group in the Old City of Jerusalem.</p>

